@startuml Activity_Wildfire_Infrastructure
title Activity Diagram - Wildfire + Infrastructure Risk

start
:Proxy /api/firms fetches MODIS/VIIRS hotspots
(bbox filtered to Turkey);
note right: poll every 5 min

:Render fire points on map layer;

:User enables pipelines overlay
(BTC, TANAP, TurkAkim, Mavi Akim,
Kerkuk-Ceyhan, Iran-Turkiye);

:Compute distance(fire, pipeline segment);

if (min distance <= proximity threshold?) then (yes)
  :Flag pipeline segment as at-risk;
  :Load related items in afet and enerji panels;
  :Raise visual alert on map;
else (no)
  :Keep fire points without alert;
endif

:User identifies fires threatening critical infrastructure;
stop
@enduml
